doctype html
html
  body
    h1 URL Shortener Microservice
    p User Stories:
    li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
    li If I pass an invalid URL that doesn't follow the valid http://www.example.com format, the JSON response will contain an error instead.
    li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

    h3 Example usage:
    p https://little-url.herokuapp.com/new/https://www.google.com
    p https://little-url.herokuapp.com/new/http://foo.com:80
    h3 Example output:
    p { "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"https://little-url.herokuapp.com/8170" }
    h3 Usage:
    p https://little-url.herokuapp.com/2871
    h3 Will redirect to:
    p https://www.google.com/